@model System.Data.DataTable
<!-- Widget ID (each widget will need unique ID)-->
@Html.Hidden("hdfIdNF", (object)ViewBag.id)
<div class="jarviswidget jarviswidget-color-blueDark" data-widget-editbutton="false">
    <div id="divData">
        <!-- end widget edit box -->
        <div class="widget-body no-padding">
            <!-- widget content -->
            <table id="dttTabela" datatables_fixedheader="top" datatables_fixedheader_offsettop="60" class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover table-click" width="100%">
                <thead>
                    <tr>

                        <th style="width:25%;">Parâmetro</th>
                        <th style="width:75%;">Valor</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    @if (Model != null)
                    {
                        foreach (System.Data.DataRow item in Model.Rows)
                        {
                            <tr role='row' id='row_@item[1]'>
                                <td>@item["Parametro"]</td>
                                <td>@item["Valor"]</td>
                            </tr>
                        }
                    }

                </tbody>
                <tfoot class="hide">
                </tfoot>
            </table>
            <!-- end widget content -->
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- end widget div -->
